                    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4">About Punjab Alumni Network</h2>
                    <p>The Punjab Alumni Network is an initiative by the Government of Punjab to create a robust
                        ecosystem connecting alumni from various educational institutions across the state.</p>
                    <p>Our mission is to foster lifelong connections between alumni, support current students, and
                        contribute to the development of Punjab through knowledge sharing, mentorship, and collaborative
                        initiatives.</p>
                    <p>This platform serves as a central hub for alumni to reconnect, network, and give back to their
                        alma mater and community.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
